  "text": "Others have used model checking and similar techniques to explore the state space of biological systems [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . In particular, we found previously that Caulobacter Crescentus was almost speed-independent [CITATION_5] (in that work, it was necessary to add a small number of timing constraints to the Caulobacter model to eliminate all hazards). However, in previous work, timing robustness appears not to have been used to critique and improve Boolean models, nor has selection pressure for speed independence been demonstrated in silico.",
